#绘制初始图像

p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat))
p

#修改每个方格的形状为圆形并映射新的颜色

col_fun <- colorRamp2(
    c(-2, 0, 2), 
    c("#8c510a", "white", "#01665e")
)
cell_fun = function(j,i,x,y,w,h,fill){
  grid.rect(x = x, y = y, width = w, height = h,gp = gpar(col = NA,fill = NA))
  grid.circle(x=x,y=y,r= percent_mat[i, j]/200 * min(unit.c(w, h)),gp = gpar(fill = col_fun(exp_mat[i,j]),col = NA))
}

p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat),col=col_fun,rect_gp = gpar(type = "none"),cell_fun = cell_fun)
p

#调整行名字体大小，将行名调整在左侧，行聚类树调整到右侧，取消列聚类

col_fun <- colorRamp2(
    c(-2, 0, 2), 
    c("#8c510a", "white", "#01665e")
)
cell_fun = function(j,i,x,y,w,h,fill){
  grid.rect(x = x, y = y, width = w, height = h,gp = gpar(col = NA,fill = NA))
  grid.circle(x=x,y=y,r= percent_mat[i, j]/200 * min(unit.c(w, h)),gp = gpar(fill = col_fun(exp_mat[i,j]),col = NA))
}
p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat),col=col_fun,rect_gp = gpar(type = "none"),cell_fun = cell_fun,cluster_columns = F,row_names_side = "left",row_dend_side = "right", row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 9))
p

#修改图例名，添加网格线、图像标题与上方行注释

col_fun <- colorRamp2(
    c(-2, 0, 2), 
    c("#8c510a", "white", "#01665e")
)
cell_fun = function(j,i,x,y,w,h,fill){
  grid.rect(x = x, y = y, width = w, height = h,gp = gpar(col = NA,fill = NA))
  grid.circle(x=x,y=y,r= percent_mat[i, j]/200 * min(unit.c(w, h)),gp = gpar(fill = col_fun(exp_mat[i,j]),col = NA))
}
cluster_anno=c(rep("Name1",3),rep("Name2",4),rep("Name3",3))
column_ha<- HeatmapAnnotation(
  cluster_anno = cluster_anno,
  col = list(cluster_anno = setNames(brewer.pal(3, "Paired"), unique(cluster_anno))
  ),
  na_col = "grey"
)

p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat),col=col_fun,rect_gp = gpar(type = "none"),cell_fun = cell_fun,cluster_columns = F,row_names_side = "left",row_dend_side = "right", row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 9),heatmap_legend_param=list(title="Average Expression" ),border ="black",top_annotation = column_ha,column_title ="Clustered dotplot")
p

#添加点的大小内容的图例

col_fun <- colorRamp2(
    c(-2, 0, 2), 
    c("#8c510a", "white", "#01665e")
)
cell_fun = function(j,i,x,y,w,h,fill){
  grid.rect(x = x, y = y, width = w, height = h,gp = gpar(col = NA,fill = NA))
  grid.circle(x=x,y=y,r= percent_mat[i, j]/200 * min(unit.c(w, h)),gp = gpar(fill = col_fun(exp_mat[i,j]),col = NA))
}
column_ha<- HeatmapAnnotation(
  cluster_anno = cluster_anno,
  col = list(cluster_anno = setNames(brewer.pal(3, "Paired"), unique(cluster_anno))
  ),
  na_col = "grey",annotation_legend_param = list(cluster_anno=list(direction = "vertical")))
lgd_list = list(
  Legend( labels = c(0,0.25,0.5,0.75,1), title = "Percent Expressed",graphics = list(
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.25 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.5 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.75 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 1 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))}
  )))
p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat),col=col_fun,rect_gp = gpar(type = "none"),cell_fun = cell_fun,cluster_columns = F,row_names_side = "left",row_dend_side = "right", row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 9),heatmap_legend_param=list(title="Average Expression",direction = "vertical" ),border ="black",top_annotation = column_ha,column_title ="Clustered dotplot")
draw(p,heatmap_legend_side = "right", 
     annotation_legend_side = "right",annotation_legend_list = lgd_list,merge_legend = TRUE)

#保存绘图结果到本地文件Dotplot-sc_Demo1.png、Dotplot-sc_Demo1.pdf中,并设置高与宽

col_fun <- colorRamp2(
    c(-2, 0, 2), 
    c("#8c510a", "white", "#01665e")
)
cell_fun = function(j,i,x,y,w,h,fill){
  grid.rect(x = x, y = y, width = w, height = h,gp = gpar(col = NA,fill = NA))
  grid.circle(x=x,y=y,r= percent_mat[i, j]/200 * min(unit.c(w, h)),gp = gpar(fill = col_fun(exp_mat[i,j]),col = NA))
}
column_ha<- HeatmapAnnotation(
  cluster_anno = cluster_anno,
  col = list(cluster_anno = setNames(brewer.pal(3, "Paired"), unique(cluster_anno))
  ),
  na_col = "grey"
)
lgd_list = list(
  Legend( labels = c(0,0.25,0.5,0.75,1), title = "Percent Expressed",graphics = list(
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.25 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.5 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 0.75 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))},
    function(x, y, w, h){grid.circle(x = x, y = y, r = 1 * unit(2, "mm"),gp = gpar(fill = "black"))}
  )))
p=Heatmap(as.matrix(exp_mat),col=col_fun,rect_gp = gpar(type = "none"),cell_fun = cell_fun,cluster_columns = F,row_names_side = "left",row_dend_side = "right", row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 9),heatmap_legend_param=list(title="Average Expression" ),border ="black",top_annotation = column_ha,column_title ="Clustered dotplot")
pdf("Dotplot-sc_Demo1.pdf",height=6,width=8)
draw(p,heatmap_legend_side = "right", 
     annotation_legend_side = "right",annotation_legend_list = lgd_list,merge_legend = TRUE)
dev.off()

     annotation_legend_side = "right",annotation_legend_list = lgd_list,merge_legend = TRUE)
